{"tid":1610719,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全部入嚟推!重要!中槍後急救處理方法&急救用品!","createTime":"2019-10-01T19:20:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T20:35:57.000Z","uid":206964,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"75482e6a5cdddd198e79a17fbe2530da3efe2145","tid":1610719,"uid":206964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:20:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">幫推！我要見到呢個post係熱門！黑警除左要還眼, 今次仲要還埋個肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n隨著第一發.38 Special打中手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 之後黑警會更加癲去用槍射手足, 所以有必要教大家基本嘅中槍後對應方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>我強烈建議大家都帶住個急救包去發夢</ins>。但係經過今次事件, 係需要帶多<ins>兩樣嘢</ins>喺你哋嘅急救包裏面！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">第一樣嘢!</span><br />\n戰術式止血帶 / 旋壓式止血帶/<br />\ncombat<br />\napplication tourniquet<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DnvL7Rd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDnvL7Rd.jpg&h=6cb1eb10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n止血帶作用係阻止四肢大量出血, 亦可以簡單咁<ins>用皮帶代替</ins>。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果四肢中槍, 就可以使用</span>, 達到止血效果, 個人建議帶<span style=\"color: red;\">兩條</span>係身, 示範影片如下:<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y81aJ81ln5Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy81aJ81ln5Q&d=0svHhEbJ%2FFd80Myex1SsDcg3oUHlS2gCMg1IFosJMKY%3D&h=cbe46829\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y81aJ81ln5Q</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">第二樣嘢！</span><br />\n胸部密封貼<br />\nHALO SEALS<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QTVDJsN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQTVDJsN.jpg&h=efffeef3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n胸部密封貼作用係封閉胸部的創口，阻止空氣從創口處進入胸腔內部, 防止導致張力性氣胸問題。當然亦可以利用常見嘅<ins>膠袋及膠布</ins>，都可以實現密封胸部創口嘅目的。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果胸部中槍, 就需要用到佢</span>, <span style=\"color: red;\">最少帶2塊係身, 最好帶4塊</span>, 示範影片如下:<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DRIH1qbUhKw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDRIH1qbUhKw&d=0svHhEbJ%2FFd80Myex1SsDcg3oUHlS2gCMg1IFosJMKY%3D&h=1df05feb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DRIH1qbUhKw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>如果真係中槍嘅話...</strong></span><br />\n如果發現你身邊嘅人或者自己中咗槍, 請立刻用你隻手用力撳住傷口, 目的係壓住傷口而減少出血過多嘅情況出現。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>情況一:</strong></span><br />\n如果中槍嘅位置喺四肢, 請使用第一樣法寶, 立即使用止血帶阻止傷口繼續大量出血, 使用完後請同時用隻手撳住傷口<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>情況二:</strong></span><br />\n如果中槍嘅位置喺胸部, 請使用第二樣法寶, <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>首先</strong></span>做一個深呼吸，係呼氣即將結束嘅時候，抹咗傷口表面滲出嘅血液，將胸部密封貼 黐喺傷口上面，並確認係黐實。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2</strong></span><br />\n如果發現子彈的出口（如果有），重複上面嘅步驟。記住一定要搜查子彈嘅出口，只係封閉一個傷口，對傷勢係完全冇任何幫助。<ins>（記住有可能出口唔只一個）</ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>3</strong></span><br />\n係處理完傷口之後，請保持坐姿或者向受傷嘅一側側臥。<br />\n<br />\n我知會好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係請記得如果唔做嘅話你或者身邊嘅人會<span style=\"color: red;\">得返20分鐘命</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎各位係下面補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">最後最後 </span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港  時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"c6b48ad38f66656e001cee6915180b076858cf28","tid":1610719,"uid":206964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:21:28.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"283259af715ffa68ecd699751e47f18a6f6ab632","tid":1610719,"uid":206964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:21:41.00